collectionMetadata.name: Number of all, Active CPF Members & Active Employers as at end of Quarter
collectionMetadata.description: Number of all, active CPF members & active employers as at end of quarter

datasetMetadata.name: Number of active employers as at end of quarter
datasetMetadata.description: An active employer refers to an employer who had paid CPF contribution for the previous month.

datasetMetadata.name: Number of active CPF members as at end of quarter
datasetMetadata.description:
An active CPF member refers to a person who has at least 1 CPF employment contribution paid for him for the current or for any of the preceding 3 months. Excludes self-employed who are not employees concurrently.
Figures are rounded to the nearest ten thousands.

datasetMetadata.name: Number of CPF members as at end of quarter
datasetMetadata.description:
A CPF member refers to a person who has a positive CPF balance in any of his CPF accounts.
Figures are rounded to the nearest ten thousands.
